}
if (typeof Q.syncIgAttitudes === 'function') { Q.syncIgAttitudes() }
!}

The tether rupture left Community Soylent and Magrail Combine willing to talk — but only through us.  Brazos Zaibatsu sits at the table too, ostensibly as a neutral party but really as a party interested in screwing them both.  They need a neutral enforcer for the ceasefire; we need to decide what that costs them.

Leverage (after crisis boost): Soylent [+ soylent_leverage +] / reprisal [+ soylent_reprisal +]; Magrail [+ magrail_leverage +] / [+ magrail_reprisal +]; Brazos [+ brazos_leverage +] / [+ brazos_reprisal +].

Any package needs **two megacorps** to accept (leverage still above reprisal after our demands).  A third who refuses may strike back immediately if their reprisal exceeds their leverage.

- @terms_menu: Review and add demands
- @finalize_deal: Close the bargain

@terms_menu
title: Terms on the table
subtitle: Pick demands, then finalize when ready
on-arrival: {!
Q.cableNegEnsureApi()
Q.cableNegSyncPolicePayReprisal()
Q.cableNegSyncCorpStances()
if (typeof Q.syncIgAttitudes === 'function') { Q.syncIgAttitudes() }
!}

