- @take_vats_police: Vats corporate police → city
- @take_railyard_police: Railyard corporate police → city
- @take_docks_police: Docks corporate police → city
- @take_limelight_police: Limelight corporate police → city
- @police_funding: Payscale for transfered police
- @corporate_tax: Tax megacorps to pay for security
- @disband_corp_police: Disband police instead of transferring
- @civil_rights: Enforce civil-rights laws again
- @ceasefire_trials: Trials for ceasefire violations
- @judge_review: Review city judges
- @infra_cap: Cap megacorp use of city infrastructure
- @prior_leverage_demands: Non-security demands (prior leverage)
- @corp_promises: Offer enticements to individual megacorps
- @withdraw_demands: Remove a demand from the package
- @finalize_deal: Close the bargain

@withdraw_demands
title: Remove a demand
subtitle: Pull terms off the table to lower corporate reprisal
view-if: cable_neg_police_vats = 1 or cable_neg_police_railyard = 1 or cable_neg_police_docks = 1 or cable_neg_police_limelight = 1 or cable_neg_police_pay > 0 or cable_neg_corp_tax > 0 or cable_neg_civil_rights = 1 or cable_neg_trials > 0 or cable_neg_judge_review > 0 or cable_neg_disband > 0 or cable_neg_soylent_education_enroll = 1 or cable_neg_magrail_education_enroll = 1 or cable_neg_brazos_education_enroll = 1 or cable_neg_soylent_education_pay = 1 or cable_neg_magrail_education_pay = 1 or cable_neg_brazos_education_pay = 1 or cable_neg_soylent_land_tax = 1 or cable_neg_magrail_land_tax = 1 or cable_neg_brazos_land_tax = 1 or cable_neg_infra_cap > 0 or cable_neg_promise_sabotage_corp > 0 or cable_neg_promise_protest_corp > 0 or cable_neg_promise_blind_eye_corp > 0 or cable_neg_promise_raid_heat_corp > 0 or cable_neg_promise_deeps_tax_corp > 0 or cable_neg_promise_docks_dmz_corp > 0

Dependent terms drop together — security tax if payroll goes; judicial review if trial rules go; tuition if enrollment goes.

- @wd_corp_tax: Withdraw security tax
- @wd_police_pay: Withdraw police payroll demand
- @wd_limelight_police: Withdraw Limelight police transfer
