@police_funding
title: Payroll for transferred police

If we absorb corporate security, someone pays them.  Without a separate demand, transferred police are assumed to stay on **city payscale (2× poverty)**.  Corporate scale is ruinous; higher city scales are merely expensive.

- @pay_city_2x: City payscale (2× poverty level)
- @pay_city_6x: City pays 6× poverty level
- @pay_city_6x_match: 6× poverty + raise city police to match
- @pay_corp_10x: Same payscale as corp security (10× poverty)
- @terms_menu

@pay_city_2x
title: City payscale (2× poverty)
choose-if: cable_neg_police_pay = 0 and (cable_neg_police_vats = 1 or cable_neg_police_railyard = 1 or cable_neg_police_docks = 1 or cable_neg_police_limelight = 1)
unavailable-subtitle: Pick a jurisdiction transfer first, or payroll already set.
on-arrival: {!
Q.cableNegEnsureApi()
Q.cable_neg_police_pay = 1
Q.cableNegSyncPolicePayReprisal()
!}
go-to: terms_menu

@pay_city_6x
title: City pays 6× poverty level
choose-if: cable_neg_police_pay = 0 and (cable_neg_police_vats = 1 or cable_neg_police_railyard = 1 or cable_neg_police_docks = 1 or cable_neg_police_limelight = 1)
on-arrival: {!
Q.cableNegEnsureApi()
Q.cable_neg_police_pay = 2
Q.cableNegSyncPolicePayReprisal()
!}
go-to: terms_menu

@pay_city_6x_match
title: 6× poverty + raise city police to match
choose-if: cable_neg_police_pay = 0 and (cable_neg_police_vats = 1 or cable_neg_police_railyard = 1 or cable_neg_police_docks = 1 or cable_neg_police_limelight = 1)
on-arrival: {!
Q.cableNegEnsureApi()
Q.cable_neg_police_pay = 3
Q.cableNegSyncPolicePayReprisal()
!}
go-to: terms_menu

@pay_corp_10x
title: Match corporate security payscale (10× poverty)
choose-if: cable_neg_police_pay = 0 and (cable_neg_police_vats = 1 or cable_neg_police_railyard = 1 or cable_neg_police_docks = 1 or cable_neg_police_limelight = 1)
on-arrival: {!
Q.cableNegEnsureApi()
Q.cable_neg_police_pay = 4
Q.cableNegSyncPolicePayReprisal()
!}
go-to: terms_menu

@corporate_tax
title: Corporate tax to fund security

We can levy a security tax on the megacorps — up to the full cost of transferred police payroll, or half if we want an easier vote.  Who pays depends on whether Brazos is exempt.

- @tax_half_belligerents: Half cost — Soylent & Magrail only
- @tax_full_belligerents: Full cost — Soylent & Magrail only
- @tax_half_all_three: Half cost — all three megacorps
- @tax_full_all_three: Full cost — all three megacorps
- @terms_menu

@tax_half_belligerents
title: Half payroll — tax Soylent & Magrail
subtitle: Brazos exempt; belligerents split the bill
choose-if: cable_neg_corp_tax = 0 and cable_neg_police_pay_effective > 0
unavailable-subtitle: Set a police payroll demand first, or tax already chosen.
on-arrival: {!
Q.cableNegEnsureApi()
Q.cable_neg_corp_tax = 1
Q.cable_neg_corp_tax_fund = 1
Q.cable_neg_brazos_tax_exempt = 1
Q.cableNegApplyTaxHalfBelligerents()
!}
go-to: terms_menu

@tax_full_belligerents
title: Full payroll — tax Soylent & Magrail
subtitle: Brazos exempt; belligerents fund all transferred police
choose-if: cable_neg_corp_tax = 0 and cable_neg_police_pay_effective > 0
on-arrival: {!
Q.cableNegEnsureApi()
Q.cable_neg_corp_tax = 2
Q.cable_neg_corp_tax_fund = 2
Q.cable_neg_brazos_tax_exempt = 1
Q.cableNegApplyTaxFullBelligerents()
!}
